messages.message: Here is the link to a project that i tried by uploading a random doc with me - a motor insurance policy and asking questions in converse app. when i ask questions about the insured car, the results are vague (would think it should tell details of model. but when i ask specific details about the car it can provide those. should the previous question have gotten these answers? project linked in thread :thread:
